              p.
                As you enter into our Gardens of Babylon, we invite you to prepare for a veritable cornucopia of sensory enchantments. The grounds boast creations to rival those for which the wondrous gardens were first renowned: let dream and reality coalesce as our mythological cast weave in and out, immersing you in such fleeting fantasies as befit a starry, midsummer night...
              p.
                Adorn yourself with verdant trappings to match even the lucent Diana and then allow yourself, upon delving into the shadowy groves, to be captured in the twinkling half-light by our roaming photographers. Throughout the adventure, revel in air ignited by the beat and flashing colours of salsa - or fly madly along to the pipes and drums of Ireland!
              p.
                And, with two stages and a tremendous variety of sparkling performers, our line-up promises to get everybody moving. Early in the evening, an elegant classical ensemble will provide the dreamy backdrop for ballroom dances. And, as the night progresses, both stages will come alive with acts ranging from vibrant jazz to buoyant a cappella - from reverberating house to fresh, intense electronic music.
            .col-lg-4.col-md-5.col-md-offset-0.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2.col-xs-12
              img.img-thumbnail.img-responsive(src='/images/entertainment1.jpg',alt='Entertainment')
          .row(style='margin-bottom:25px;')
            .col-lg-4.col-md-5.hidden-sm.hidden-xs
              img.img-thumbnail.img-responsive(src='/images/entertainment2.jpg',alt='Entertainment')
            .col-lg-8.col-md-7.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
              p.
                When the sun starts to rise and twilight turns to morning, you’ll be reinvigorated by the unfolding of a silent disco - with two beautiful DJs keeping you dancing through dawn. And, were that not enough, after 3am our second stage will become a hub of graceful acoustic artists, and a whole plethora of comedians...allowing you to sit back and relax amongst the creeping tendrils of the Gardens - all without having to move a muscle. 
              p.
                Whatever your taste, and whatever your pleasure, we’ll have you enraptured and enthralled. Simply immerse yourself in our Eastern paradise; complete with fortune-tellers, shisha, magic, music and mysteries galore. On the 26th June, Oriel births an assemblage of spectacles sublime – sure to result in a night of a thousand-and-one quite singular memories.
