          .row(style='margin-bottom:25px;')
            .col-lg-8.col-md-7.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
              p.
                Once more, Oriel brings you the commemoration ball of the year - and all the drinks to befit it. Commence your night with the finest champagne and the fruitiest Pimms in our beautiful First Quad, along with some delectable canap&eacute;s&hellip; before indulging in the most delicious cocktails all night from our many bars, serving classical favourites alongside a rather special Oriel Ball concoction.
              p.
                If cocktails are not what you&rsquo;re after then never fear: naturally, we are supplying an abundance of exotic teas, creamy milkshakes, and refreshing juices to keep you hydrated throughout the night.
              p.
                For those who want to try a bit of everything - and why not? - we&rsquo;ll have wine and beer bars to quench even the most Sisyphean thirsts, providing exceptional quality (in exceptional quantity) as you meander through our Gardens of Babylon. You will also be able to try some of the finest whiskies available, as you lose yourself betwixt serene surrounds.
              p.
                As the night slides into daybreak and you find yourself lusting for a quick pick-me-up, grab some piping-hot coffee and tuck into breakfast.
              p.
                Expect only the most delicious drinks, from the familiar to the foreign. And, for the discerning, there might even be some surprises&hellip;          
